se.softhouse.common.strings

Interface Describer<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type to describe
    All Superinterfaces:
    Function<T,String>

    @Immutable
public interface Describer<T>
extends Function<T,String>
    Describes values of the type T (or subclasses of T). Useful when Object.toString() doesn't give you what you want.
    See Also:
    Describers
